headline: GTA Online
subtitle: Discounts
content:
Those looking to become Smugglers and cargo traffickers can purchase any Hangar, plus their renovations, upgrades, and modifications, for 40% off this week.

Meanwhile, there's 40% off the Buckingham Alpha-Z1 and a range of other vehicles on sale, including:

- Mammoth Tula – 30% off
- JoBuilt Velum 5 Seater – 30% off
- Sea Sparrow – 40% off
- Nagasaki Ultralight - 40% off

And More! Check out the Rockstar Newswire for more details.
